      "date": "2020-01-20 02:45:06.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+2\n\n> fsx: test_fallocate: filesystem does not support fallocate mode 0x0, disabling!\n > fsx: test_fallocate: filesystem does not support fallocate mode 0x3, disabling!\n > fsx: test_fallocate: filesystem does not support fallocate mode 0x10, disabling!\n > fsx: test_fallocate: filesystem does not support fallocate mode 0x1, disabling!\n\nIt looks like this is working properly to detect that fallocate is not working for the unpatched client, which is good.",
